
Project : Task Tracker

links: https://pythonhosted.org/Flask-JWT/

1. Task has following fields:

		Task_ID
		Task_Name
		Task_Desc
		owner (user_name)
		owner_id (user_id)
		Due date
		child_tasks
		parent_tasks

2. User has following fields:

		user_name
		password
		user_id

3. APIs to be developed:

POST /<IP>/Task/<Task_name> /* User authentication required*/
PUT  /<IP>/Task/<Task_name> /* User authentication required*/
GET  /<IP>/Task/<Task_name> /* User authentication required*/
DELETE /<IP>/Task/<Task_name> /* User authentication required*/

GET /<IP>/Task_list

POST /<IP>/User
DELETE /<IP>/User
